category.description:
The mobile games or no app games are constituted for offering the online gaming experience to good number of touch screen devices including as smart phone, PDA, Tablet Computer and portable media player and other such devices. The very first version of the online mobile game played with no download  by most of the players is snake game.

However, the free mobile games that at are being played now-a-days are either downloaded from apps stores or one can play them from mobile game operators portal. There are many other ways too as handheld devices, memory card and handset with cable that offer facilities too.

The current generation of games run on different platforms including Palm OS, Symbian, Adobe Flash Lite, Jio Games, Windows Mobile, Apples iOS and Googles Android. Most of the online games are prepared using the Unity gaming engine. Online monetisation modes for online gaming are pay-per-load, subscription, free-to-play and advertising supported.

Due to the limitation of memory space and hardware infrastructure the mobile games generally tends to be very small and short. Therefore, many a times these games come without any much information and pre-review of the gaming apps.Virtual Reality game is another popular genre of online gaming app that is pacing up to according to the need of contemporary players of modern times. In the augmented reality games a device having a reverse facing camera is being used to generate effects and the player enjoy the game through the device camera and lense. Online mobile games are also being enjoyed and played in multiplayer mode as well. Some of the popular mode of online games with us include Fitness workout XI, Crime Hunt 3D, Little Brain Doctor, Galaxy Force, Path of Hero, Street Racer, Gods of Arena and other games.
